s project is a Vim configuration  dedicated.

Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/mtanguy/dotvim.git ~/.vim


    Create symlink:

 ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc


   Install packages:

 sudo aptitude install git exuberant-ctags ruby1.8-dev rake


  Switch to the `~/.vim` directory, and fetch submodules:

  cd ~/.vim
  git submodule sync
  git submodule init
  git submodule update
  git submodule foreach git submodule init
  git submodule foreach git submodule update
                                        
                                    
  Compile command-t:
  cd ~/.vim/bundle/command-t
  rake make
